ygData.subject: Ranger/Woodelf needs guidance.........
ygData.msgSnippet: Hello Ladies, I am a lvl 12, almost 13, Ranger/Woodelf residing in North Quynos and wanted to know if anyone has any secrets, hints or anything of where to go
ygData.messageBody:
Hello Ladies,

I am a lvl 12, almost 13, Ranger/Woodelf residing in North Quynos and wanted to know if anyone has any secrets, hints or anything of where to go for some GOOD hunting.  I am tired of the scenery in NQ and need a new residence, any ideas that won't get me slaughtered??? LOL

Also weapons are key! Do you know of any quests that i might do to get a new improved weapon? Oh yes, and if you are ever wandering around NQ tell me, i am Melefante, if you pick up any rusty weapons i can sharpen them for you, i bought a few too many sharp stones, hahahhahaha.  I am trying to get rid of them wisely!

Email me anytime,

~Melefante
